        "text": {
          "status": "extensions",
          "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n  <table class=\"narrative-table\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th colspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Metadata</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Title</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">ImagingStudyFeasibilityTest</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Version</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">1.0.0</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Topic</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">FHIR\r\n</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Topic</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">CQL\r\n</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Steward (Publisher)</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">Balgrist</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Description</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\"><div><p>Imaging Study Feasibility Test</p>\n</div></td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Type</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<td class=\"content-container\">\r\n    logic-library from <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-library-type.html\">http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/library-type</a> \r\n\r\n\r\n</td>\r\n\r\n\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<tr>\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n  \r\n\r\n<th scope=\"row\" class=\"row-header\">Dependency</th>\r\n\r\n\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  <td class=\"content-container\">\r\n    \r\n    <em>Description</em>: Code System DICOM\r\n    \r\n    <br/>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <em>Resource</em>: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir